videos.headline: Max Borghi runs in opening TD for Washington State
videos.description: Washington State takes the lead over Arizona thanks to Max Borghi's 26-yard TD run.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Max Borghi crosses goal-line for 26-yard Rushing touchdown) 2021/11/20 ESHEET

videos.headline: De Laura finds Harris for Washington State's second TD
videos.description: Jayden de Laura hits Travell Harris in stride for the eight-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Travell Harris hauls it in for 8-yard Receiving TD) 2021/11/20 ESHEET

videos.headline: Boobie Curry gets Arizona on the board with 11-yard TD
videos.description: Arizona cuts the deficit in half thanks to Boobie Curry's diving TD catch.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Boobie Curry hauls it in for 11-yard Receiving touchdown) 2021/11/20 ESHEET

videos.headline: Calvin Jackson Jr. snags 43-yard TD catch for Washington State
videos.description: Jayden de Laura throws another dime as Washington State takes a 21-7 lead at the half.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Calvin Jackson Jr. scores 43-yard Receiving TD vs. Arizona) 2021/11/20 ESHEET

videos.headline: Borghi punches in his second TD for Washington State
videos.description: Max Borghi is now tied for second-most touchdowns all time in Washington State football history, putting the Cougars up 28-7.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Max Borghi breaks off 13-yard rush vs. Arizona) 2021/11/20 ESHEET
